# Fundamentos de Programación

### Sintaxis y Semántica

```mermaid
flowchart LR

A["Variables y tipos de datos"]

A --> P
A --> C
A --> S

subgraph P["Primitivos"]
direction TB
P1["Enteros"]
P2["Decimales"]
P3["Booleanos"]
P4["Caracteres"]
P5["Nulo/Vacío"]
end

subgraph C["Compuestos"]
direction TB
C1["Cadenas"]
C2["Arrays/Listas"]
C3["Objetos"]
C4["Tuplas"]
end

subgraph S["Sistemas de tipos"]
direction TB
S1["Tipado estático"]
S2["Tipado dinámico"]
S3["Tipado fuerte"]
S4["Tipado débil"]
end
```

### Operadores

```mermaid
flowchart LR

A["Operadores"]

A --> M
A --> C
A --> L
A --> S
A --> B
A --> T

subgraph M["Aritméticos"]
direction TB
P1["+"]
P2["-"]
P3["*"]
P4["/"]
P5["%"]
P6["**"]
end

subgraph C["Comparacion"]
direction TB
C1["=="]
C2["!="]
C3["<"]
C4[">"]
C5["<="]
C6[">="]
end

subgraph L["Lógicos"]
direction TB
L1["AND"]
L2["OR"]
L3["NOT"]
end

subgraph S["Asignación"]
direction TB
S1["="]
S2["+="]
S3["-="]
S4["*="]
S5["/="]
end

subgraph B["Bit a Bit"]
direction TB
B1["AND"]
B2["OR"]
B3["XOR"]
B4["NOT"]
end

subgraph T["Ternario"]
direction TB
T1["AND"]
T2["OR"]
T3["NOT"]
end

```

